cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to improve temporal ordering of events in text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of deep learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of embeddings, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of synthetic data, which could suggest it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
